snippet.title: Meet the Pyro
snippet.description:
The masked arsonist known only as "Pyro" has always been the most unknowable of the Team Fortress mercenaries. Until now. Today the mask comes off. Metaphorically. That's right: It's time to Meet the Pyro.

Team Fortress 2 is Free to Play. For more information about the game, visit our website: http://www.teamfortress.com

Get the free download of Team Fortress 2 for Mac or PC on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/440/
